lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;马努斯（Manus）进行了Openai：&lt;/strong&gt;中国人工智能创业公司Manus &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/5HKxfuWHeUuaUn-cON1lulQiEykV4R6THGmc8hYiyBmKIm6lzbxt6494KTPjGtMqulGB7TsedeKEkZ5sruCODnFO2onBTrYusbTW9PuyWLUzLe1tJduOeORzlQp3a6H8TVTyH5a3SUVqauOl68_A92IMU4aKoUig-Gm2Xe77s6crjK60nxZMWKtbj3exa8UxSLNZtkhEmEqYuqq4JK5TXw0EMa6GTfRDC0QiPHz04b7ShoQWHvZDH-NXGYLe6uFmUYMDO5fI8CL4QTakbBCMWjU5CA/Qj_SQfmMaB4BgSU5hEuUH-zDLvf1oi4j/9" target="_blank"&gt;推出了&lt;/a&gt;文本与视频生成功能，使其与OpenAI，Alibaba和Tencent等竞争对手的更具成熟的工具直接竞争。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Pornhub在法国变黑：&lt;/strong&gt; Pornhub，YouPorn和Redtube的母公司，在该国的新时代验证要求上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ZaVsTctd0UKtYqOPxJTyCzxZk_gHNBYRf2ZXGMmh0RT95AYkYHjNNfoSZAcCcfGqZcPQaCjIqs3bA2pinlIFrKfXhbVeidbsLSWwOEyuhsSuUokUr2g8qOJxq9qPx8d1cMGIjgQ3xaOJ1f-wYU7mUyfn39WOX3aLuGGKjZiHhrRvj_0qStnKtmX61N4b4kcoLWYysew5xblHGhnq8vz-MFG2Yo32J1fM1exTd5aSTWk7gFESdqD1xT-QrCf285UkHOJybkB6L5VWZCHP94eupdcl-w/6tayLKuYf2rUX64qE4I_nZnA0lfcmC7T/9" target="_blank"&gt;封锁了其成人内容的访问&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;Microsoft的高管改组：&lt;/strong&gt; LinkedIn的首席执行官&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/io_vjSjSEybY6fVEbzNBO0cDgmtTrntdzwb7fM19WcLIwnqPNiW8voujCTH0_s2HLgndilmPEXfE_DMdMS4XHY4xtV3tYJ8hqMKng7Ewxkoy_9g33WmuGiltVu3PUiWu9D0N66YkdKCDOnxkF5jxLaElijQ8bMGUNxnk86785aFBKJ7UpuWNU8DinTAjqg5Zx7lADHSSKtx-A2fjD50XCkugHg_9uMIo